The Spirit of This License
Parkroad Fellowship provides this software and its associated documentation as an intentional act of Christian stewardship. Our conviction is that the tools we develop for the Gospel should be shared freely to empower the global Church and mission organisations. Consequently this resource is offered without charge to fellow ministry organizations so that they may adapt, deploy and utilize it for their specific callings. Because we view this work as our humble contribution to society and the Body of Christ we strictly prohibit its commercialization by any party.


